title: Victorian review (F1214)
abstract: Rushes of green, open country, a farmer, a river and sheep.
description: Rushes.  1. Green and open property, following a farmer on a red tractor and sheep. Overcast and dull weather.  2. Shots of a river/river banks and lanscape shots of mountains and clouds.  3. A large truck carries a house along a dirt road near a river.  4. Footage of a quary with bulldozers.  5. River.  6. Tractor pulling a machine this is cutting grass/crops.  7. Close-ups shot in a studio of various bugs climbing on the ends of branches. Also close-ups of an orange with maroon spots.
